WEBVTT

00:00:30.476 --> 00:00:32.553
Zoh, a hawidang a kawh cang hna,

00:00:32.577 --> 00:00:34.577
Nan hngalh khawh ahcun,
apakhatnak zultu

00:00:34.601 --> 00:00:37.976
zei ah rel lomi santlailo 
dirhmun ah chiah asi khi.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:39.976
Hitin um khawh dingah ralthatnak aherh.

00:00:40.484 --> 00:00:44.976
hmasabik hruaitu khi hawidang hna
hruaitu ah sertu taktak cu asi.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:46.976
(Nihthawng)

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:50.221
(Kutbenghthawng)

00:00:50.245 --> 00:00:51.976
Cun, tucu pahnihnak 
zultu a ra cang.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.398
Tucu, santlailo pahnih an um cang--

00:00:54.422 --> 00:00:56.976
Pathum cu mibu an si cang,
i mibu cu thawngpang a si.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:58.976
Cucaah, cawlcanghnak cu 
zapi he aa san.

00:00:59.343 --> 00:01:02.576
Hruaitu lawng siloin zultu hna 
hmaisuam ve zong abiapi,